-- Factbox: ConocoPhillips global production areas
-- 
-- Thu Jul 14, 2011 9:14am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/14/us-conocophillips-production-factbox-idUSTRE76D2UJ20110714

 

 (Reuters) - ConocoPhillips ( COP.N ) plans to separate its exploration and production business from its refining and marketing business, turning itself into two stand-alone, publicly traded companies. 

 Last year the integrated energy company produced 1.752 million barrels of oil equivalent per day. Below is the distribution of its oil and gas production around the world. * Lower 48 United States 25 percent * Europe 20 percent * Canada 16 percent * Asia Pacific/Middle East 16 percent * Alaska 14 percent * Africa 6 percent * Russia 3 percent (Source: ConocoPhillips 2010 annual report)